snippet.title: NIGHTSIDE launch trailer
snippet.description:
NIGHTSIDE LAUNCH TRAILER

http://nightsiderts.com/

http://store.steampowered.com/app/360390

NIGHTSIDE is a sci-fi base building real time strategy game set on the dark side of an unknown planet where the valuable "green ice" resource can be found.
